{"tid":2151385,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男工涉踢防暴 斥警屈打成招","createTime":"2020-08-11T11:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T11:15:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"00ddc8ac7c660f46efc75e28988f439dbe6d2a46","tid":2151385,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/6ZCCQAY6A6CO6JT7XUEDXXLX3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F6ZCCQAY6A6CO6JT7XUEDXXLX3A%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=bd579560\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F6ZCCQAY6A6CO6JT7XUEDXXLX3A%2F&h=50d0778c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/6ZCCQAY6A6CO6JT7XUEDXXLX3A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n男工涉踢防暴 斥警屈打成招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xDJAErW9GjzPQY7nygxDX7tzYHI=/640x497/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZWHABND4MOQC56VC7UEHKLPRMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxDJAErW9GjzPQY7nygxDX7tzYHI%3D%2F640x497%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZWHABND4MOQC56VC7UEHKLPRMY.jpg&h=0569e398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年10月1日市民在港鐵太子站外將立法會議員何君堯的相片貼在地上，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被踢落樓梯 腦癇症發作<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨指任職運輸工的被告盧家業（42歲）是遭警方屈打成招，警署內被警員辱罵，威脅指有片段拍下他犯案，會送他到新屋嶺；叫他解鎖電話不果後，有警員將其電話摔在地上，並從後踢他令他跌落樓梯，繼而多人用警棍打他的背、用圓盾鋤心口，再向他施以胡椒噴霧。被告要求入院，警員表明「唔錄口供唔可以入院」。患腦癇症的被告在沒服藥、一度病發的情況下作第二次會面錄影。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱被襲警員梁偉嘉昨供稱，當日他在警署候命，有同事稱外面有警長受襲，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當日站在梁身後的警員盧俊傑則稱，見被告表現出「想離開現場」後他即以襲警罪拘捕對方，因被告激動反抗，他兩次以警棍打被告左大。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3815/19"},{"pid":"1c759094a7c885e04b3610520657c654d3cbfff7","tid":2151385,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab4cdd25f303e285a345dff2f6906bb9b3e2a58","tid":2151385,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">警員盧俊傑</span></span>"},{"pid":"c1a2ad724268c48e81e378744b9715c235dcc787","tid":2151385,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:15:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">聲稱被襲警員梁偉嘉</span></span>"}]}